 jenkins th senate f thompson • b frist house b gordon • b clement • j duncan jr • j tanner • e bryant • v hilleary • z wamp • h ford jr • w jenkins th senate b frist • l alexander house b gordon • j duncan jr • j tanner • z wamp • h ford jr • w jenkins • j cooper • m blackburn • l davis th senate b frist • l alexander house b gordon • j duncan jr • j tanner • z wamp • h ford jr • w jenkins • j cooper • m blackburn • l davis authority control worldcat identities viaf  lccn n gnd  ndl  us congress f retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlebillfristoldid categories  birthsstcentury american politiciansamerican presbyteriansamerican surgeonsfrist familyharvard medical school alumnihospital corporation of america peopleintelligent design advocatesliving peoplepeople from nashville tennesseephilanthropists from tennesseerepublican party united states senatorstennessee republicanstheranos peopleunited states senators from tennesseevanderbilt university facultywoodrow wilson school of public and international affairs alumnihidden categories webarchive template wayback linksall articles with dead external linksarticles with dead external links from november articles with permanently dead external linkspages with citations lacking titlespages with citations having bare urlsarticles with dead external links from june blp articles lacking sources from april all blp articles lacking sourcesall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from may articles needing additional references from may all articles needing additional referenceswikipedia articles needing clarification from may wikipedia articles with viaf identifierswikipedia articles with lccn identifierswikipedia articles with gnd identifiers navigation menu personal tools not logged intalkcontributionscreate accountlog in namespaces article talk variants views read edit view history more search navigation main pagecontentsfeatured contentcurrent eventsrandom articledonate to wikipediawi